title: HPI Spencer
content: The patient is a follow-up for her previous condition. She reports improvement in motion and desires suture removal. Incision is clean and intact.

title: Musculoskeletal
content: Range of motion of the finger near full without pain, no evidence of triggering, moderate ecchymosis consistent with post-operative state.

title: Plan
content: Sutures removed today. Follow-up in 4 weeks.
